                      "description": "<p>a closure that can set optional <a href=\"#/p5/preload\">preload()</a>,\n                             <a href=\"#/p5/setup\">setup()</a>, and/or <a href=\"#/p5/draw\">draw()</a> properties on the\n                             given p5 instance</p>\n",
